## 📊 Data Flow Architecture

```mermaid
flowchart TB
    subgraph Frontend
        A[Excel Import Page] -->|POST /api/excel/submit| B[Cloud Server]
        C[Settings Page] -->|PUT /api/admin/organization/eta-settings| B
        D[Settings Page] -->|POST /api/settings/save| B
    end

    subgraph Cloud Server
        B --> E{Build & Sign Invoice}
        E -->|Agent Bridge| F[OTax Agent on PC]
        E -->|PFX Cloud| G[PFX Signer]
        F -->|Signed Doc| H[Submit to ETA]
        G -->|Signed Doc| H
    end

    subgraph Database
        H -->|Save| I["public.documents"]
        H -->|Save| J["InvoicesDb.org_N_*_documents ← NEW"]
        D -->|Save| K["LoginDb.clients_info_new"]
        C -->|Save| L["LoginDb.organization_settings"]
    end

    subgraph Dashboard
        M[Dashboard API] --> I
        M --> J
        N[ETA Sync] -->|Populate| J
    end
```

