## ✅ Testing Checklist

After deployment, verify the following:

- [ ] **Log out and log back in** — Required for JWT fix to take effect
- [ ] **Save Settings** — Should succeed without hwid error
- [ ] **Test Connection (PreProd)** — Should return success with valid credentials
- [ ] **Test Connection (Prod)** — Should return success with valid credentials
- [ ] **Submit Invoice from Excel** — Should:
  - [ ] Read issuer data from org table
  - [ ] Sign via agent bridge
  - [ ] Submit to ETA successfully
  - [ ] Save to `public.documents`
  - [ ] Save to `"InvoicesDb".org_N_*_documents`
- [ ] **Dashboard** — Should show submitted invoices
- [ ] **Agent logs** — Should show clean registration without JWT errors

